  "text": "All teachers believed that authentic materials for teaching reading can increase their students' vocabulary knowledge [CITATION_1] . They offer wide range of vocabularies. Students can expand their knowledge of how to use the words in appropriate contexts. Teachers noted that authentic texts motivate students to acquire new words. It is often found that authentic texts use a different variety of text structures.",
